    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">3–12</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Letter length range</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>The real power of -AL is volume — with 800+ options, you'll almost always have an -AL word available from any rack. Words like PHYSICAL and MYSTICAL pair common roots with high-value letters (Y=4, PH=7) for strong mid-range scores.</p>

